      <h3 class="hca-text--title">Time</h3>
      <br />
      <div class="site-section">
        <h4 class="hca-text--body-2">From the HCA Enterprise Content Style Guide</h4>
        <br />
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <div class="site-container--body-content">
              <p class="hca-text--body-1">In content, time should be expressed as a figure followed by “a.m.” or “p.m."</p>
              <p class="hca-text--body-1">Use noon or midnight rather than 12 p.m. or 12 a.m., which can be easy to misunderstand. For times that are not at the top of the hour, use colons, i.e., 1:30 p.m.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
