            <div class="site-container--body-content">
              <p class="hca-text--body-1">When presenting a timestamp it is important to present it in numerical format.</p>
              <p class="hca-text--body-1">If you are using a 12-hour timestamp:
                <ul class="site-list site-list--bulleted">
                  <li class="site-list__item">Display the hour and minutes separated by a colon (11:00 PM)</li>
                  <li class="site-list__item">Use uppercase AM or PM with no periods (This saves precious UI space)</li>
                  <li class="site-list__item">Do not use leading 0s for hours under 10</li>
                </ul>
              </p>
